      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented in exemplary showroom condition, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector. Every aspect of this specimen, from its flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a standard of maintenance that is beyond reproach. Mechanically sound and aesthetically impeccable, this motorcar offers an uncompromising experience for those who demand the finest in automotive preservation.",
