    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it garage-kept and spotless. If you're looking for perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
      "price": 44900.0,
