    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S featuring the iconic wide-body silhouette and an impeccable mechanical pedigree. This 996.2 is powered by a 3.6L flat-six utilizing VarioCam Plus for optimized valve timing across the rev range. The M96 power plant has been fortified with a dual-row ceramic IMS bearing retrofit and a fresh rear main seal, ensuring long-term reliability. Power is delivered through a precise G96 6-speed manual transaxle to the sophisticated all-wheel-drive system. The chassis remains taut with factory-calibrated Bilstein dampers, while the braking system features four-piston monoblock Brembo calipers over cross-drilled rotors. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the interior retains its factory matte finish with no bolster wear. A surgically clean example for the discerning collector.",
